Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.62,0:22:47.04,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}ほら、見て　愚かな駒よ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.04,0:22:52.09,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}断罪の茶番
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.17,0:22:54.84,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}独壇場Funky
