Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.98,0:23:10.69,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}叫べ　My Justice，Right Way
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.69,0:23:13.07,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Make it a vow!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.07,0:23:15.70,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}感心できるのはFunky
