Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.46,0:23:26.08,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}鮮烈過ぎた年回
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.17,0:23:28.25,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}偏見のあるカテゴライズ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.25,0:23:30.46,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Don't believe no story
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.46,0:23:32.51,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}I know you're ready
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.51,0:23:34.38,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}No, we're already over
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.38,0:23:36.38,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Everybody loves despair
