Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.57,0:22:31.24,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}高舉白旗的奇蹟
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.74,0:22:36.99,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在逃獄後的歡呼聲中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.99,0:22:41.16,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}被強行拷上了手銬
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.62,0:22:47.04,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}看吧 愚昧的棋子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.04,0:22:52.09,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這定罪的把戲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.17,0:22:54.84,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}奇異的獨角戲舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.84,0:22:57.51,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}用你的眼睛看著 競爭
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.56,0:23:02.60,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}{\fad(200,200)}遺落
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.51,0:23:02.60,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}欺騙吧 Close Enough
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.60,0:23:05.19,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}多線並行的發展
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.19,0:23:07.98,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}撥開人群
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.98,0:23:10.69,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}呼喊著 這是我正義的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.69,0:23:13.07,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}許下你的誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.07,0:23:15.70,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}值得讚美的驚恐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.70,0:23:18.41,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}唯獨拒絕喪失
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.41,0:23:23.41,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}指引我吧 Close Enough
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.46,0:23:26.08,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}過於艷麗的忌日
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.17,0:23:28.25,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}帶有偏見的分類
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.25,0:23:30.46,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不要相信沒有故事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.46,0:23:32.51,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我知道你準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.51,0:23:34.38,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不 我們已經結束了
